{"tid":1581283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"921和理非獅鳥入","createTime":"2019-09-19T13:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:45:01.000Z","uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"311ab517a4cf6b2cd3158dc9699c5029925c5038","tid":1581283,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"守連儂牆係必要既 但守既方法千變萬化<br />\n因為兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n就算你叫人唔好去，到最後都一定會有人去<br />\n我地不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆<br />\n只極大量既和理非人數先可以保護勇武！<br />\n我地甚至可以一起舉傘幫手擋雨<br />\n記住一點 Be water 有咩事狗唔會幫我地<br />\n物係死 人係生 但都要出咗黎睇定先！"},{"pid":"91771bf0c31863005add1a307a6959528cb7e36e","tid":1581283,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=5ee1b840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"02f8d203812708586e5987507d5ad00faa292006","tid":1581283,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"一齊e爆林鄭，去&ldquo;社區對話&rdquo;寧願黃絲入去都唔好俾班維穩五毛入去圍爐！<br />\n<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/had056/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fhad056%2Ftc%2F&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=cee79b35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/had056/tc/</a>"},{"pid":"846d386189f850466750c41294edcc896a117d60","tid":1581283,"uid":21545,"like":1,"di